title: Allows farm service and non-residential customer-generators to designate 100% of wind generated credits
summary: Allows farm service and non-residential customer-generators to designate 100% of wind generated credits to meters owned by such customer-generator and being within 25 miles of the wind electric generating equipment.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the public service law, in relation to remote metering by farm service and non-residential customer-generators
